      "text": "No audio packages installed. I need to install them. But first, let me understand the user's request better. They want to make the karaoke track sound studio-quality. I should:\n\n1. Convert the Opus file to WAV for processing\n2. Apply professional audio processing:\n   - Normalize levels - Apply EQ to enhance the piano sound\n   - Add compression for consistent volume\n   - Possibly add reverb for studio feel\n3. Convert back to a high-quality format (WAV or FLAC) for playbackLet me create a plan and then implement it.",
