      "type": "thought",
      "text": "Great! Now I have ffmpeg available. Let me create a professional audio processing script. I'll:1. Convert the Opus file to WAV (lossless)2. Apply professional audio processing:\n   - Normalize levels\n   - Apply EQ to enhance the piano sound\n   - Add compression for consistent volume\n   - Add subtle reverb for studio feel\n3. Convert back to high-quality WAV/FLAC\n\nLet me create the script now.",
