q=-1.0 size=    9216KiB time=00:03:54.00 bitrate= 322.6kbits/s speed=15.6x elapsed=0:00:14.97    \rframe=14503 fps=936 q=-1.0 size=    9728KiB time=00:04:01.94 bitrate= 329.4kbits/s speed=15.6x elapsed=0:00:15.49    \rframe=14933 fps=933 q=-1.0 size=    9984KiB time=00:04:09.11 bitrate= 328.3kbits/s speed=15.6x elapsed=0:00:15.99    \rframe=15437 fps=935 q=-1.0 size=   10240KiB time=00:04:17.52 bitrate= 325.7kbits/s speed=15.6x elapsed=0:00:16.51    \rframe=15944 fps=936 q=-1.0 size=   10496KiB time=00:04:25.98 bitrate= 323.3kbits/s speed=15.6x elapsed=0:00:17.03    \rframe=16326 fps=931 q=-1.0 size=   10752KiB time=00:04:32.35 bitrate= 323.4kbits/s speed=15.5x elapsed=0:00:17.54    \rframe=16882 fps=935 q=-1.0 size=   11008KiB time=00:04:41.63 bitrate= 320.2kbits/s speed=15.6x elapsed=0:00:18.06    \rframe=17338 fps=932 q=-1.0 size=   11264KiB time=00:04:49.23 bitrate= 319.0kbits/s speed=15.5x elapsed=0:00:18.60    \rframe=17708 fps=926 q=-1.0 size=   11520KiB time=00:04:55.41 bitrate= 319.5kbits/s speed=15.4x elapsed=0:00:19.12    \rframe=18133 fps=922 q=-1.0 size=   11776KiB time=00:05:02.50 bitrate= 318.9kbits/s speed=15.4x elapsed=0:00:19.66    \rframe=18623 fps=923 q=-1.0 size=   12032KiB time=00:05:10.67 bitrate= 317.3kbits/s speed=15.4x elapsed=0:00:20.17    \r[out#0/mp4 @ 000001ed80165980] video:2693KiB audio:9821KiB subtitle:0KiB other streams:0KiB global headers:0KiB muxing overhead: 3.491265%\r\nframe=19079 fps=931 q=-1.0 Lsize=   12951KiB time=00:05:18.36 bitrate= 333.2kbits/s speed=15.5x elapsed=0:00:20.48    \r\n[aac @ 000001ed82131900] Qavg: 0.303  Tr: 2.0%  TNS(L): 1.3%  TNS(S): 18.8%  M/S: 8.5%  I/S: 0.0%  PNS: 0.0%\r\n",
