      "code": "{\"command\": \"Remove-Item \\\"C:\\\\Users\\\\LLM-Test\\\\Downloads\\\\Anna_Karaoke_Video.f298.mp4\\\" -Force -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\\nRemove-Item \\\"C:\\\\Users\\\\LLM-Test\\\\Downloads\\\\Anna_Karaoke_Video.f140.m4a\\\" -Force -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\\nGet-Item \\\"C:\\\\Users\\\\LLM-Test\\\\Downloads\\\\Anna_Karaoke_Lyrics_Video.mp4\\\" | Select-Object Name, Length\", \"description\": \"Clean up temp files and check final video\"}",
