      "text": "## Videos Ready for Anna! \n\n**Files Created:**\n- `C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\Downloads\\Anna_Karaoke_Lyrics_Video.mp4` (12.6 MB)\n- `C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\Downloads\\Anna_Karaoke_Lyrics_Enhanced.mp4` (12.6 MB - speaker optimized)\n\n---\n\n### **What Anna Gets:**\n\n| File | Video | Audio | Best For |\n|------|-------|-------|----------|\n| **Lyrics_Video.mp4** | 720p60 (lyrics visible) | Original quality | Phone screen |\n| **Lyrics_Enhanced.mp4** | 720p60 (lyrics visible) | Speaker-optimized | Bluetooth speakers |\n\n---\n\n### **For Anna to Use:**\n\n1. **Send her the video file via WhatsApp** - it's only 12.6 MB\n2. **She can watch the lyrics on her phone screen**\n3. **Connect phone to Bluetooth speakers** for playback\n4. **The enhanced version** has:\n   - Boosted vocal clarity (2.5kHz)\n   - Reduced low-end rumble\n   - Consistent volume levels\n\n---\n\n### **Quick Send via WhatsApp:**\n\nRight-click the file → Share → WhatsApp → Select Anna\n\nThe video shows lyrics on screen so she can sing along while the audio plays through her speakers! 🎤",
