      "text": "Now I understand - **Anna is a professional performer** at corporate events (like Lancome) with song requests. This needs a **enterprise-grade playback system**.\n\n---\n\n### **What She Needs:**\n\n| Requirement | Why It Matters |\n|-------------|----------------|\n| **Instant search** | Guest requests \"Alicia Keys\" - find in 2 seconds |\n| **Consistent audio** | No volume jumps between songs |\n| **Professional quality** | Lancome-level brand standards |\n| **Quick load** | No buffering/delay when switching tracks |\n| **Backup system** | Never fail at a live event |\n\n---\n\n### **Let Me Build Her Professional System:**",
