      "type": "thought",
      "text": "The user is telling me that Anna performs at events (like Lancome events) and gets song requests. This is a professional karaoke/business scenario. I need to understand what she needs:\n\n1. A professional catalogue system for corporate events\n2. Quick song request fulfillment\n3. Consistent quality across all tracks\n4. Easy playback systemLet me help build this professional system for her.",
